<h2>Welcome to Keelfin!</h2>

<p>Hi <%= @resource.name.present? ? @resource.name.split(' ').first : 'there' %>,</p>

<p>Thanks for signing up! You're one step away from taking control of your financial future. Please confirm your email address to get started.</p>

<p style="text-align: center;">
  <a href="<%= confirmation_url(@resource, confirmation_token: @token) %>" class="btn">Confirm my email</a>
</p>

<div class="note">
  <strong>What's next?</strong> Once confirmed, you'll set up your monthly income, choose your spending categories, and start tracking your finances like a pro.
</div>
